  <brief_title>Study of a Treatment Driven by Early PET Response to a Treatment Not Monitored by Early PET in Patients With AA Stage 3-4 or 2B HL</brief_title>
  <acronym>AHL 2011</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase III Study of a Treatment Driven by Early PET Response Compared to a Treatment Not Monitored by Early PET in Patients With Ann Arbor Stage III-IV or High Risk IIB Hodgkin Lymphoma</official_title>
